Package: magma-sidecar
Version: 0.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd, acl, libc6
Maintainer: Hydrogen Labs <ops@hydrogenlabs.xyz>
Homepage: https://github.com/MagmaStaking/magma-sidecar
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/MagmaStaking/magma-sidecar.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/MagmaStaking/magma-sidecar
Description: Magma Sidecar - tip-based MEV reprioritization for Monad
 Co-located sidecar for a Monad validator. Connects to the node's txpool IPC
 socket and re-injects MagmaSearcherGateway traffic with a tip-derived priority
 so the node orders MEV-relevant transactions ahead of vanilla traffic. Searchers submit to the node's
 JSON-RPC directly. Companion to the upstream Monad node's txpool IPC protocol;
 see /usr/share/doc/magma-sidecar for details.
